\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Head turned towards the door. Low hum, ravaneous horde. Glint of firelight on their backs like a swarm of hornets.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Um\u8230\'85I don\u8217\'92t have enough in me for all of them.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Ayramun what that meant.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Elrahet screamed, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Run!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri slowest.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 As he running. Heart exploding in his chest.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Mandri.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What!?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Remember what you said about friendship?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Obo, what in the white light\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 \u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m going to prove something to you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Hops off.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri running away.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Moto, moteah, and Purl cut them with swords. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Demons ran right past them.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 All to Obo.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 it clicked. The conversation. He\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d said no one. He wasn\u8217\'92t about to let Obo prove him wrong. Grab Obo and not let him do it.}
