\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 As if the sl. Time was slipping, Mandri had the. Frozen. As before, in the Goree Pass. The rainbowed light of purpose.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 An urge, again to paint. A glorious scene. Figures in such as only artists could dream, a diorama of flesh, flame, and butchery. Threading through his eye.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 He was crying, eyes wide, tears overflowing his lid. Not for his mother. Not for himself. He cried for Obo.}
